###
# Filter posts with maxPrice (price <= 100)
GET http://localhost:5000/post?maxPrice=100

###
# Filter posts with minDays and maxDays (3 <= numberOfDays <= 7)
GET http://localhost:5000/post?minDays=3&maxDays=7

###
# Filter posts by country
GET http://localhost:5000/post?country=USA

###
# Filter posts by city and country
GET http://localhost:5000/post?city=NewYork&country=USA

###
# Combined filters: price, days, and location
GET http://localhost:5000/post?maxPrice=500&minDays=2&maxDays=10&country=USA

###
# Filter with pagination
GET http://localhost:5000/post?maxPrice=1000&page=1&batchSize=10

